title: The Pricks @ Funk 4 Free
description:
Arnette All Night Antics featuring The Pricks. Funk 4 Free was a concert in Costa Mesa, CA. with The Pricks, Bukue and Del the Funky Homosapien.

Big thanks to Tiki Bar and Arnette
